name: Nanbai

reviews.review_text:
We were on the lookout for an artisanal café for lunch and were fortunate to stumble upon this gem.

The ambiance was clean, bright, and well-lit, with both indoor and outdoor seating options available.

The food we had was absolutely delicious. From the chicken croissant to the bagel, everything was fresh and flavorful. Don’t miss their crafted chocolates and ice cream—especially the caramel ice cream, which was simply out of this world.

The staff were friendly and attentive, though the service was a bit slow. We had to wait over 35 minutes for our order to be served.

All in all, it’s a great spot to relax and enjoy some truly tasty food.

A nice cafe located below Palm Air hotel. They have a nice seating arrangement inside and outside the cafe. We have visited this place a couple of times during our stay in Goa and it did not disappoint. We had the English breakfast, coffee, pastries, tea, juice, fries, gelato and other exciting items. They were really good!

During our recent trip to Panjim, Goa, we set out to find a standout café to unwind, and NANBAI kept popping up with great reviews. Trusting the buzz on Google, we decided to give it a go.

The café ambiance was charming, radiating a relaxed vibe that makes it perfect for unwinding or a casual hangout. The décor was thoughtfully designed, adding a cozy touch that was both inviting and stylish. We ordered a mocha and a hot chocolate, and both drinks impressed us with their quality—smooth, rich, and flavorful. The mocha was perfectly brewed, and the hot chocolate had that luxurious creaminess that’s hard to beat.

However, while the quality was spot-on, the prices seemed on the higher side. For the portion sizes, it felt a bit steep, though perhaps that’s the trade-off for the premium ingredients and chic vibe.

All in all, NANBAI was a pleasant experience—a great spot for a delicious dessert or a quality coffee break. While a tad over-rated in our opinion, it’s certainly worth a visit for anyone looking to experience an upscale café in Panjim.

description:
**Discovering Nanbai: A Culinary Jewel in Goa**

Nestled in the vibrant heart of Goa, Nanbai boasts an impressive 4.5-star rating, backed by over 1,160 enthusiastic reviews from delighted patrons. This charming café has quickly become a favorite among locals and travelers alike, with popular tags such as "puffs" (25), "almond croissant" (18), "gelato" (16), and "prawn" (12) highlighting its diverse culinary offerings.

### Ambiance & Design

As you step into Nanbai, you're greeted by a clean, bright interior that perfectly balances a relaxed and sophisticated vibe. With thoughtful décor, including comfortable seating arrangements both indoors and al fresco, the café invites visitors to unwind and savor their experience. The atmosphere is enhanced by ambient lighting and a stylish design, creating an inviting space reminiscent of both a chic café and a cozy escape. The buzz of conversation marries well with the inviting scent of fresh pastries, as evidenced by the vibrant customer photos depicting lush greenery and tasteful art pieces that adorn the walls.

![Nanbai Interior](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmsS-5z-QZfhrC0eaEsncbtx4aaL_a8ASOwzNfd3k9F7bsClCMeV4kB1yGtQn9Z17yj5or522RNIbfshGJOs4Z4TCse5NQJpw-1FJ1eqBVic4jzQ2RjdO_Lyjhn_qNK8j8YLgs=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Nanbai is a true eclectic mix that caters to diverse tastes. Signature items such as the renowned almond croissant and freshly made puffs consistently garner praise from diners. Customers rave about the creamy gelato—particularly highlighting flavors that promise to intrigue your palate as well as delight your sweet tooth. Diners enjoyed treats ranging from chicken croissants to bagels, each dish noted for its freshness and flavor.

Reviewers have painted vivid pictures of both the food and drink presentations. For instance, the mochas and hot chocolates were described as “smooth, rich, and flavorful,” showcasing the café’s dedication to high-quality ingredients. While some found prices a tad steep, others defended it as a reflection of the gourmet experience offered.

### Customer Experience & Service

A visit to Nanbai may introduce diners to both friendly, attentive staff and a slice of the laid-back Goan lifestyle. However, service speed appears to be a point of contention, with some guests noting longer wait times for their food—reaching up to 35 minutes during peak hours. Despite this, many agree that the quality of food makes the wait worthwhile, affirming Nanbai's status as a location worthy of any culinary adventure.

### Popularity & Reviews

Social media buzz and word-of-mouth have played a significant role in establishing Nanbai as a must-visit spot in Goa. Customers often share their experiences on platforms, reinforcing the sentiment that this café is a delightful destination for both locals and tourists. Despite some critiques regarding portion sizes versus prices, the overall sentiment remains overwhelmingly positive. Patrons fondly recall their visits and often express anticipation for their next meal at this delightful establishment.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Stunning images shared by customers capture the essence of Nanbai’s inviting ambiance and delectable culinary offerings. From beautifully plated croissants and artful gelato creations to cozy seating arrangements—every photo tells a story of taste and relaxation. It’s a visual experience that promises to complement the dining experience, ensuring that Nanbai remains etched in memory long after you leave.

![Food Presentation at Nanbai](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkPW6G_f5dxKy5cfEEUvKxCJXuwGBV3CaQP57ks_L5nVfk_2-8465MAoK3wwU6K_KD5tWgDP9X9SkifvcCb8vsdK--qJu04-LfYzO3ETMad376nMcgPBJiAlk7qD0Vr5uqfmWEZ4w=w375-h281-p)

In conclusion, Nanbai stands out not just for its flavor-packed menu but also for its warm atmosphere, making it a prime destination for those eager to taste the delights of Goan café culture. Whether for a casual coffee date, a hearty breakfast, or a sweet post-lunch treat, Nanbai invites you to indulge in its many offerings, promising an experience that resonates with each visit.
